WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.550 align:middle line:10%
- In a first of its kind study,
the psychoactive drug MDMA

00:00:05.550 --> 00:00:07.770 align:middle line:10%
was just shown to
be exceptionally

00:00:07.770 --> 00:00:10.110 align:middle line:10%
effective in
treating alcoholism,

00:00:10.110 --> 00:00:12.750 align:middle line:10%
offering new hope
for a frustratingly

00:00:12.750 --> 00:00:16.290 align:middle line:10%
difficult to treat condition.

